text: Rémi Santiago (born 10 December 1980) is a French ski jumper. He competed in the large hill event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Chambéry
